    "Again, the Pareto fronts are visualized (Fig. 5f), showing that the optimal solutions from the model with pretraining consistently outperform those from the model without pertaining.",
    "In this study, we compare and benchmark advanced deep generative AI models to learn the complex language of polymers, enabling the generation of promising electrolyte candidates.",
